properties.name: Quail Ridge Off Leash Area
properties.description: Posted by WestcomapiI-70 at Hwy 40, Wentzville, MOLocated in the Quail Ridge County Park. Open to the public. From Highway 40, turn west at Callahan Rd. then take an immediate right onto the south service road also called Quail Ridge Parkway. Follow for approximately .8 of a mile. Turn left into the park and drive straight on Paw Paw Dr. until it ends in a parking lot. The OLA will be on the left.
